<li id="cite_note-vaishnava-160"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-vaishnava_160-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="../K.A._Nilakanta_Sastri" title="K.A. Nilakanta Sastri" class="mw-redirect">K.A. Nilakanta Sastri</a>, <i>The CōĻas</i>, p 681</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-vedic-161"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-vedic_161-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><i>Purananuru</i> (poem 224) movingly expresses his faith and the grief caused by his passing away.</span></li>
